'''Addae Tuntum''' (Akwasidae Tuntum) Afahyɛ yɛ afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Achensua – Asutifi wo Ahafo Mantam, kane Bono ne Ahafo Mantam wɔ Ghana no di<ref>https://www.graphic.com.gh/features/features/brong-ahafo-region-still-feeding-the-nation.html</ref>. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a edikan<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref> anaa nea ɛtɔ so mienu no mu<ref>https://blastours.com/west-africa-travel-destinations/regions-of-ghana/ghana-festivals/61-akwasidae-tuntum-festival</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammere ntade ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi saa Afahye yi de kae ɔsa a ɛde Ebirimoro a ɛkɔɔ so wɔ Sefwie ne Ahafo nam wo afeha a etɔ so 18 no mu<ref>https://www.blastours.com/west-africa-travel-destinations/regions-of-ghana/ghana-festivals/61-akwasidae-tuntum-festival</ref>. Wosan nam saa aahye yi so de kyerɛ sɛ wotaa won ahenfo no akyi.<ref>https://www.ghanaconsulatedubai.com/tourism.html</ref>

